title: Joe Satriani: Surfing With The Alien Legacy Edtion [DVD Rip]
description:
In 2007, the Legacy Edition of Joe Satriani's masterpeice, "Surfing With The Alien", was released. It had remastered audio and came with a DVD featuring a never before released concert, Montreux Jazz Festival on 6/15/1988, with Joe performing with bassist Stu Hamm and drummer Jonathan Mover. Ive checked this site to see if anyone released it, didnt find it, so here it is :]

Setlist:

1. Ice 9
2. Memories
3. Midnight
4. Rubina
5. Circles
6. Lords of Karma
7. Stu Hamm bass solo
8. Echo
9. Hordes of Locusts
10. Always With Me, Always With You
11. Satch Boogie

Enjoy!
